{"tid":2230744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗暗示短期內推健康碼","createTime":"2020-10-05T06:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T07:14:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6dee73adbf768843513fbaae8d7cafe12dd632ef","tid":2230744,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/Z2GWMNV5DBC5ZPPYV2HOPDEQGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FZ2GWMNV5DBC5ZPPYV2HOPDEQGI%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=e43d64a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FZ2GWMNV5DBC5ZPPYV2HOPDEQGI%2F&h=2565666b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/Z2GWMNV5DBC5ZPPYV2HOPDEQGI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n張建宗暗示短期內推健康碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ldG41LXjBZka4ZTTb6w7UXl5bCo=/1212x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WVCI3W4ANBBPBIPDC6A6DYMNUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FldG41LXjBZka4ZTTb6w7UXl5bCo%3D%2F1212x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWVCI3W4ANBBPBIPDC6A6DYMNUA.jpg&h=7f060cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■張建宗指讓持證明內地港人免檢回港的研究進入最後階段。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政務司司長張建宗表示，政府正積極與內地及澳門商討健康碼機制，並透露當局研究讓持有相關證明的內地港人免檢疫回港，已進入最後階段，意味有關安排或於短期內推出。不過，中大前校長、現任中大醫學講座教授沈祖堯認為，疫苗及有效藥物面世前，政府必須守住關口。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：與同鄉逛海港城 泰婦確診  IVE男家人感染 警查涉事酒吧有否聘黑工<br />\n<br />\n張建宗昨在網誌指出，港府正積極與內地和澳門商討，讓持有武肺病毒核酸檢測陰性證明的人士，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沈祖堯：有疫苗前須守關口<br />\n<br />\n張建宗稱，近期疫情有所紓緩，但仍然反覆，呼籲市民繼續保持高度防疫意識，避免疫情再次在社區爆發，令過去兩個多月的努力付諸流水。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：隔離時發病 尼泊爾婦傳親友<br />\n<br />\n2003年沙士期間。。。。。。。。。，而且沙士的死亡率高，患者不會周圍走，傳播風險較小。<br />\n<br />\n沈祖堯指，沙士抗疫只用了三個月，但形容今次疫情是疲倦及漫長的戰爭。沈續稱，大部份武漢肺炎患者病徵輕微、年輕患者死亡率低，認為在疫苗或有效藥物面世前，最有效的控制方法是隔離及預防，認為政府須多做檢測、守住關口。"},{"pid":"fc68251ca7f240e0cc33e4489767bca7c033326c","tid":2230744,"uid":349505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"其實仲有好多公公婆婆唔係用智能手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cadca4dc43927780c6a2c08487334173ee3ae3","tid":2230744,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"唔down冇得出國旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d8b624c4e374f22da259d52a99448d3104b52d","tid":2230744,"uid":300262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"張建宗有冇死屋企人 唔記得"},{"pid":"101efb5e470fdd69d24f6c84938bfad433583f98","tid":2230744,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"有健康碼唔使疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcb548a9dd1e352c479736efdee081f9d2c9309","tid":2230744,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"陳雲又中  一早屌人恐懼撚"},{"pid":"2d0bf7161c8fec55bca28c486e773cd3d04ff790","tid":2230744,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"否則好難一車車落來投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f34325a7e8638991fe09559c6096a7de98952e8","tid":2230744,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />mola mola"},{"pid":"0b9ea755a9dd43c5282da790641097a1302c10f1","tid":2230744,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"